wm-commonstrings-aboutme: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content providing information about the individual contributing
wm-commonstrings-activities: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content related to an entity's happenings
wm-commonstrings-agenda: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content related to an entity's meeting agenda
wm-commonstrings-background: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content with historical or summary information on a given topic
wm-commonstrings-bylaws: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content related to an entity's governing document
wm-commonstrings-closed: String commonly used in timelines or documentation to indicate a topic is closed
wm-commonstrings-conclusion: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content providing summary or final assessment of the main topic
wm-commonstrings-connect: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content with ways people can engage with other individuals on the main topic
wm-commonstrings-contacthuman: String commonly used in navigation or headers to invite people to contact an actual human primarily responsible for main topic
wm-commonstrings-contactus: String commonly used in navigation or headers to invite people to contact individuals or entities primarily responsible for main topic
wm-commonstrings-enterquestion: String commonly used as a label prompting people where to provide text of a question they have
wm-commonstrings-events: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content about activities happening related to the main topic
wm-commonstrings-externallinks: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content with links to external websites related to the main topic
wm-commonstrings-follow: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content providing ways people can follow the topic or individual on social media
wm-commonstrings-mainarticle-prompt:
String commonly used in navigation or hatnotes to label an article which contain the main content on the related topic

Parameters:
* $1 - Local link to main content article with information on the related topic
* $2 - Number of articles
wm-commonstrings-mainpage-prompt:
String commonly used in navigation or hatnotes to label a page which contain the main content on the related topic

Parameters:
* $1 - Local link to main content page with information on the related topic
* $2 - Number of pages
wm-commonstrings-mywork: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content describing the contributing individual's work or activities
wm-commonstrings-news-events: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content about activities happening or news items related to the main topic
wm-commonstrings-noticeboard: String commonly used in navigation or headers for areas of content containing notices or messages
wm-commonstrings-objectives: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content about the aims and goals of the main topic
wm-commonstrings-ongoing: String commonly used in timelines or documentation to indicate a topic is ongoing
wm-commonstrings-open: String commonly used in timelines or documentation to indicate a topic is still open
wm-commonstrings-overview: String commonly used in navigation or headers for a summary of the main topic
wm-commonstrings-participate: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content with ways people can engage with the main topic
wm-commonstrings-please-remember:
String commonly used in labels to prompt someone to remember to take actions described in subsequent text

Parameters:
* $1 - Text of reminder
wm-commonstrings-policies-guidelines: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content related to an entity's official policies and guidelines
wm-commonstrings-projects-collaborations: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content related to an entity's activities and efforts as well as their work with partnered entities or individuals
wm-commonstrings-purpose: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content providing the thinking or reasoning behind the main topic
wm-commonstrings-questions: String commonly used in navigation or headers to indicate where people can seek answers to questions
wm-commonstrings-register-account: String commonly used in navigation, buttons, or headers to encourage people to register an account
wm-commonstrings-reports: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content about reports or documentation relevant to the main topic
wm-commonstrings-resolutions:
String commonly used in navigation or headers for resolutions officially adopted by an entity or governing body

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of resolutions
wm-commonstrings-scope: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content about the scope of the main topic
wm-commonstrings-seealso: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content with additional information on the main topic
wm-commonstrings-shortcut:
String commonly used in captions to label a page serving as an alias link for a longer pagename

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of links
wm-commonstrings-staff: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content about individuals working professionally for or on the main topic
wm-commonstrings-talktous: String commonly used in navigation or headers to prompt feedback or discussion
wm-commonstrings-updates: String commonly used in navigation or headers for content providing new information related to the main topic
